API to use: https://docs.developer.yelp.com/docs/fusion-intro
Ideas:
  - Determine popular vacation spots by looking at reviews for various categories of businesses such as:
      - Food
      - Hotels & Travel
      - Arts/Entertainment
      - Active Life

Use these ratings to show the top 3(?) cities in each continent for travel destinations

Show a dropdown with the cites to allow the user to select up to 3-4 cities to compare, allow selection of the subcategories to be explores (hotels, restaurants, etc.)

Click on the markers to show name and rating and other Yelp info

Display bar charts to visualize ratings of the selected categories

Focus on one specific price range, to lessen the amount of data and pings to the API
